title: 11/21: Start or Sit (AFC); Rankings Disputes (Fantasy Football Podcast)
description:
Revisiting the IND-HOU game which we previewed yesterday. We’ve got some updated injury information and some updated thoughts on the game. We’ll also take a look at some players who might need to be added and are widely available (7:50) like David Njoku, Benny Snell and N’Keal Harry … Giving you all the news updates you can handle (14:00)! Who’s in? Who’s out? Then we’ve got some stats to know for Week 12 (18:35) including how good the LAR run defense has been recently. And Dave, Jamey and Heath get into some rankings debates (20:42)! Baker Mayfield, Cooper Kupp, Tom Brady and more! … DAL-NE (29:00), PIT-CIN (40:40), OAK-NYJ (48:40), BAL-LAR (56:10), DEN-BUF (1:01:20), JAC-TEN (1:05:00), MIA-CLE (1:09:30) … Email us at fantasyfootball@cbsi.com
